span.font: Kabi's responsibility includes the integration of three APIs for handling job postings, developed by the Naukri-India team. These APIs encompass functionalities for creating, updating, and deleting job posts.

div.font: When job seekers apply to job postings on Naukri's India portal, it is Naukri India's responsibility to transmit candidate information to Kabi's ATS via an API. This API performs the following actions:

div.style: font-size: 13px;
font-size: 13px;

span.font: - Creates a user and application in the ATS if they do not already exist.

div.style: font-size: 13px;

span.font:
- Modifies candidate existing information based on a flag received from Naukri India, and then creates an application for the candidate.
Explained in the flowchart below.
